originalText.text: I moved from utter frustration to empathy for the lone staff member.. when discovered that the Kenyan GOVERNMENT has ONE staff member working the WHOLE division. WHere the Heck does the money in tax we pay for go if they can't afford to have ample staff for more effecient running? Someone must digg into this . It is Not right!

originalText.text: I never write reviews, but the office in NYC is bordering on embarrassment. Their staff can never provide any information without giving an attitude and being rude. Their default is "go to the website". Well if the website was so clear why the hell would I be calling?? Ive traveled alot and called several other embassies and never get this rude behavior from others. Now, with the E-passport debacle, it's amazing Kenyans have to take vacation time to travel to DC or LA to get the darn thing done.
